        "tab-1": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "DESCRIPTION",
            "content": "<p>Keraclear is a doctor-formulated antifungal nail serum that penetrates through the nail bed to fight fungus at its source. Our proprietary oil-based formula delivers clinically-studied ingredients like Tea Tree Oil and Undecylenic Acid deep into the nail matrix where creams and polishes can't reach. Made in the USA with 100% natural ingredients.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab-2": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "INGREDIENTS",
            "content": "<p><strong>Tea Tree Oil</strong> — Powerful natural antifungal that penetrates the nail bed.<br><strong>Undecylenic Acid</strong> — FDA-recognized antifungal from castor oil.<br><strong>Vitamin E</strong> — Nourishes damaged nail tissue and supports new growth.<br><strong>Jojoba Oil</strong> — Restores moisture and enhances absorption.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab-3": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "THE SCIENCE",
            "content": "<p>Keraclear was developed by Dr. Landford, a board-certified dermatologist with 25+ years of clinical experience. The formula is based on peer-reviewed research showing that oil-based delivery systems penetrate the nail plate 4x more effectively than water-based creams. Each ingredient has been independently studied for its antifungal properties.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab-4": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "SHIPPING AND GUARANTEE",
            "content": "<p><strong>Free Shipping</strong> — All orders ship free from the USA via USPS.<br><strong>Fast Delivery</strong> — Orders ship within 24 hours. Delivery in 3-5 business days.<br><strong>90-Day Guarantee</strong> — If you're not satisfied, contact us for a full refund. No questions asked.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
